News / 07.20.2017
RURAL CHINA: TRANSFORMING LIVES THROUGH BETTER VISION
Since 2015 Essilor’s Vision Ambassador program has created 2,000 new primary vision care providers to bring affordable eye care across Asia, Africa and Latin America.

 






 
News / 07.13.2017
SUSTAINABILITY: COSTA SUPPORTS SHARK AND OCEAN RESEARCH

Costa continues its commitment to protecting ocean habitats with the launch of its new OCEARCH sunglasses collection.

 






 
News / 07.06.2017
ESSILOR ENGAGES CONSUMERS IN A GLOBAL VIRAL CAMPAIGN AGAINST AGE CONDITIONING
With the #AgeIsJustANumber campaign, Varilux®, Essilor’s progressive lens brand, sets out to create a different outlook on aging. 

 






 

Combination of Essilor and Luxottica
Essilor and Delfin, the majority shareholder of Luxottica Group, announced on January 16, 2017 the signing of an agreement designed to create an integrated global player in the eyewear industry with the combination of Essilor and Luxottica. You will find in the following page all the information related to the combination project.

 









