discover our key jobs






As the only pure player dedicated to ophthalmic optics and present in 69 countries, Essilor Group offers a wide variety of business roles – from marketing and finance, to sales and R&D. It’s a palette of opportunities that’s constantly growing, as the Group’s field of activity expands.












Sales 

At Essilor group, we aim to go beyond a simple sales relationship with customers and create a real partnership with each of them. The sales function is at the heart of this challenge.

 Read more  
  











Marketing 

The marketing function contributes to the Group’s growth by meeting customer and consumer needs and expectations.

 Read more  
  











Finance 

Joining the Essilor group in a management and finance role is all about investing your experience in a dynamic, international and fast-growing publicly listed company.

 Read more  
  











R&D 

A lens is a high-tech product integrating many technologies. Being part of the R&D team is an opportunity to participate in the continuous improvement of the Essilor group’s products to best meet our customer expectations.

 Read more  
  











Production 

The international nature and scope of Essilor’s supply chain enables the Group to offer a varied and stimulating career path for production teams.

 Read more  
  

















